### 1. Register a Patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/patients/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
  "medicalHistory": "No known allergies."
}

### 2. Add a Doctor
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Smith",
  "email": "dr.smith@example.com",
  "specialization": "Cardiology",
  "available": true
}

### 3. Book a Successful Appointment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/book?patientId=1&doctorId=1&appointmentTime=2026-07-20T10:00:00&symptoms=Routine checkup

### 4. Test Double-Booking Prevention (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/book?patientId=1&doctorId=1&appointmentTime=2026-07-20T10:00:00&symptoms=Duplicate slot check

### 5. Fetch All Appointments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments